dct_title_s: Carte particulière des côtes de France : (partie comprise entre Bayonne et la côte d'Espagne)
dct_description_sm: Scale [ca. 1:3,000,000]. Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Shows coast of France from Bayonne to Fontarbie. In upper right-hand corner : N° 177. Historic Maps copy has paper labels on verso: "French Coast from Bayonne to the Spanish Frontier" and "No. 771."
dct_publisher_sm: [Paris] : Publiée par ordre du Roi ... au dépôt-général de la marine, 1829.
